last_episode_to_air.overview: The banker is revealed as one last contestant vies for the biggest prize in Deal or No Deal history.

name: Deal or No Deal Island
overview: A new twist on the classic game that follows contestants to the banker’s private island, where they must compete in tough challenges to find hidden briefcases worth over $200 million -- then try to beat the banker in “Deal or No Deal.”

episodes.name: Are You a Gambler?
episodes.overview: Thirteen players gather on the elusive banker's private island to hunt for briefcases worth more than $200 million in hopes of being the last contender standing.

episodes.name: Are You Calculating?
episodes.overview: Shots are fired on the elusive banker's private island as the remaining 12 players fracture into alliances. The pressure rises as one player makes a move and gets closer to the biggest prize in Deal or No Deal history.

episodes.name: Are You Fearless?
episodes.overview: The 11 remaining players compete at dizzying heights. With tensions high, a fight breaks out as one player makes a game-altering decision.

episodes.name: Are You Intuitive?
episodes.overview: The banker assesses whether one of the remaining 10 players can bluff their way into securing the highest-value briefcase, bringing them closer to the largest prize in Deal or No Deal history.

episodes.name: Are You Trustworthy?
episodes.overview: Failing the banker's test of trust could eliminate one of the remaining nine players from the pursuit of the largest prize in Deal or No Deal history.

episodes.name: Are You Intentional?
episodes.overview: The remaining eight players continue their quest for the largest Deal or No Deal prize in history. Explosive drama unfolds as the banker presents a game-changing personal offer.

episodes.name: Are You Decisive?
episodes.overview: The island's tranquility shatters when tensions boil over and personalities clash in the players' pursuit of the largest prize in Deal or No Deal history.

episodes.name: Are You Meticulous?
episodes.overview: The remaining seven players must navigate a tangled web in their hunt for the largest prize in Deal or No Deal history as one member struggles after the loss of a key alliance.

episodes.name: Are You Ruthless?
episodes.overview: A critical error has the potential to upend the game and terminate one player's quest for the largest prize in Deal or No Deal history.

episodes.name: Are You Powerful?
episodes.overview: Power trumps money as the last five players strategically target each other and make crucial moves to advance to the final four.

episodes.name: Are You Tenacious?
episodes.overview: A shocking turn of events rocks the game for the final four competitors.

episodes.name: Can You Beat the Banker?
episodes.overview: The banker is revealed as one last contestant vies for the biggest prize in Deal or No Deal history.
